The fuzziness of morning and her heavy hangover slowly began to slip away and she became more alert. Paren wasn't here... He was here last night... wasn't he? Yes, yes he was. Hmm... She sipped her water regularly and glanced idly around. Boots on the floor. Bags. Pants. Pillow. Backpac-PANTS?! How did her pants get on the floor?! She looked down at her legs to see skin! Those WERE her pants. On the floor!! ...but why. PAREN, that's why! that dirty snake!! All that Hoku had on was her shirt and undershorts. Thank god she at least had SOMETHING on. Why... if she wasn't so blasted this morning, she'd walk right outta here and beat the life outta that man!! But... she was pretty blasted... and walking just wasn't appealing. So... she'd wait till he got back to the room and... maybe yell at him for a bit... or at least raise her voice a little. Whichever worked out first.<br>
<br>
~*(it's blah, but oh well)*~ <p><br>
